com.plexus.sam.gui.models
Class DynamicPlaylistModel

java.lang.Object
  com.plexus.sam.gui.models.DynamicPlaylistModel

public class DynamicPlaylistModel
extends java.lang.Object

This model is used in the GUI to edit and display a dynamic playlist. It is possible to set and get the name and relevance properties, and listeners are being notified of changes in these properties.

plexus
